动能

$$T = \frac{1}{2}\int_0^{L}\rho(\frac{\partial y}{\partial t})^2 dx$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T dt &amp;= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \int_0^L \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial t} dx \right) dt = \int_0^L \left( \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial t} dt \right) dx \\
&amp;= \int_0^L \left( \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \delta y \right) \Bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} dx - \int_0^L \left( \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} \delta y dt \right) dx \\
&amp;= - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \int_0^L \rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} \delta y dx \right) dt
\end{align*}
$$


势能

$$ V = \int_0^L T(x)(ds -dx) + \frac{1}{2}k y^2 |_{x=L}$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta V &amp;= \int_0^L T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial x} \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t) \\
&amp;= \int_0^L \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \frac{\partial}{\partial x} (T \delta y) \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t)\\
&amp;= T \left. \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right|_0^L \delta y - \int_0^L \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) \delta y \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t) \\
&amp;= \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \Bigg|_{x=L} \delta y - \left. T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right|_{x=0} \delta y - \int_0^L \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) \delta y \, dx
\end{align*}
$$

由 Hamilton 原理

$$\int_{{t_1}}^{{t_2}} {\delta T - \delta V{\rm{ + }}\delta {W_{nc}}{\rm{d}}t} = 0$$

则有

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left\{ \int_0^L \left[ -\rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} + \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) + f \right] \delta y \, dx - \left. \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \delta y \right|_{x=L} + \left. T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \delta y \right|_{x=0} \right\} dt &amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

方程为

$$-\rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} + \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) + f = 0$$

边界条件

$$\left.\delta y \right|_{x=0} = 0$$

$$\left. \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \right|_{x=L} = 0$$

令$y = Y(x)e^{i \omega t}$,y有

$$
\frac{{{\partial ^2}Y\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}} + \omega ^2Y\left( x \right) = 0
$$

解为

$$Y(x) = A \sin \omega x + B \cos \omega x$$

代入边界条件有

$$
\begin{align*}
B &amp;= 0 \\
(k \sin (\omega L) + T \omega \cos (\omega L))A + (-T \omega \sin (\omega L) + k \cos (\omega L)) B &amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

由行列式为0,得

$$k \sin (\omega L) + T \omega \cos (\omega L) = 0$$

不妨令$T = k L$, 有

$$\sin (\omega L) + L \omega \cos (\omega L) = 0$$

解得

$${\omega_0}L = 0,\;\;{\omega_1}L \approx 2.02876,\;\;{\omega_2}L \approx 4.91318,{\rm{ }}{\omega_3}L \approx 7.97867$$

## 3.1

动能

$$T = \frac{1}{2}\int_0^{L}\rho(\frac{\partial y}{\partial t})^2 dx$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \delta T dt &= \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \int_0^L \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial t} dx \right) dt = \int_0^L \left( \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial t} dt \right) dx \\
&= \int_0^L \left( \rho \frac{\partial y}{\partial t} \delta y \right) \Bigg|_{t_1}^{t_2} dx - \int_0^L \left( \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} \delta y dt \right) dx \\
&= - \int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left( \int_0^L \rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} \delta y dx \right) dt
\end{align*}
$$


势能

$$ V = \int_0^L T(x)(ds -dx) + \frac{1}{2}k y^2 |_{x=L}$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\delta V &= \int_0^L T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \frac{\partial \delta y}{\partial x} \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t) \\
&= \int_0^L \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \frac{\partial}{\partial x} (T \delta y) \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t)\\
&= T \left. \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right|_0^L \delta y - \int_0^L \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) \delta y \, dx + k y(L, t) \delta y(L, t) \\
&= \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \Bigg|_{x=L} \delta y - \left. T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right|_{x=0} \delta y - \int_0^L \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) \delta y \, dx
\end{align*}
$$

由 Hamilton 原理

$$\int_{{t_1}}^{{t_2}} {\delta T - \delta V{\rm{ + }}\delta {W_{nc}}{\rm{d}}t} = 0$$

则有

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_{t_1}^{t_2} \left\{ \int_0^L \left[ -\rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} + \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) + f \right] \delta y \, dx - \left. \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \delta y \right|_{x=L} + \left. T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \delta y \right|_{x=0} \right\} dt &= 0
\end{align*}
$$

方程为

$$-\rho \frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2} + \frac{\partial}{\partial x} \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} \right) + f = 0$$

边界条件

$$\left.\delta y \right|_{x=0} = 0$$

$$\left. \left( T \frac{\partial y}{\partial x} + k y \right) \right|_{x=L} = 0$$

ds - dx &= \sqrt{dx^2 + \left(\frac{\partial y}{\partial x}\right)^2 dx^2} - dx \\

## 3.2

令$y = Y(x)e^{i \omega t}$,y有

$$
\frac{{{\partial ^2}Y\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}} + \omega ^2Y\left( x \right) = 0
$$

解为

$$Y(x) = A \sin \omega x + B \cos \omega x$$

代入边界条件有

$$
\begin{align*}
B &= 0 \\
(k \sin (\omega L) + T \omega \cos (\omega L))A + (-T \omega \sin (\omega L) + k \cos (\omega L)) B &= 0
\end{align*}
$$

由行列式为0,得

$$k \sin (\omega L) + T \omega \cos (\omega L) = 0$$

不妨令$T = k L$, 有

$$\sin (\omega L) + L \omega \cos (\omega L) = 0$$

解得

$${\omega_0}L = 0,\;\;{\omega_1}L \approx 2.02876,\;\;{\omega_2}L \approx 4.91318,{\rm{ }}{\omega_3}L \approx 7.97867$$

主振型

$$Y_i(x) = \sin \omega_i x$$
